{"nodes":[{"content":"NoNewLine parameter","pos":[2,21]},{"pos":[22,157],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Out-File<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>, <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Add-Content<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>, and <bpt id=\"p3\">**</bpt>Set-Content<ept id=\"p3\">**</ept> now have a new <bpt id=\"p4\">**</bpt>–NoNewline<ept id=\"p4\">**</ept> switch which simply omits a new line after the output.","source":"**Out-File**, **Add-Content**, and **Set-Content** now have a new **–NoNewline** switch which simply omits a new line after the output."},{"pos":[431,507],"content":"Without <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>–NoNewline<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> specified, each fragment would be on a separate line:","source":"Without **–NoNewline** specified, each fragment would be on a separate line:"}],"content":"# NoNewLine parameter\n**Out-File**, **Add-Content**, and **Set-Content** now have a new **–NoNewline** switch which simply omits a new line after the output.\n```PowerShell\nPS C:\\> \"This is \" | Out-File -FilePath Example.txt -NoNewline\n\nPS C:\\>; \"a single \" | Add-Content -Path Example.txt -NoNewline\n\nPS C:\\> \"sentence.\" | Add-Content -Path Example.txt -NoNewline\n\nPS C:\\> Get-Content .\\Example.txt\n\nThis is a single sentence.\n```\nWithout **–NoNewline** specified, each fragment would be on a separate line:\n```PowerShell\nPS C:\\> \"This is \" | Out-File -FilePath Example.txt\n\nPS C:\\> \"a single \" | Add-Content -Path Example.txt\n\nPS C:\\> \"sentence.\" | Add-Content -Path Example.txt\n\nPS C:\\> Get-Content .\\Example.txt\n\nThis is\n\na single\n\nsentence.\n```\n"}